{"tid":1922290,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(派成績表) 六大發展商口惠實不至長實拒減租　新地玩拖延","createTime":"2020-03-12T13:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T13:15:07.000Z","uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25d9dc4735f66de05b64a99254ea921471a42872","tid":1922290,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"新地真係最撚萬惡 打鑼打鼓話減租拿光環<br />\n之後全部租戶交完盤數 話唔撚減<br />\n依幾個月又狂放警察入場拉手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200312/PNH6YOIX2WDISDXWKEQCC3DUOI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200312%2FPNH6YOIX2WDISDXWKEQCC3DUOI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=bea06ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200312%2FPNH6YOIX2WDISDXWKEQCC3DUOI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=309a11c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200312/PNH6YOIX2WDISDXWKEQCC3DUOI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情令本港零售及服務業迎來「超級寒冬」，各大地產商上月紛紛表明會減租助租戶抗逆境；不過本報走訪本港六大發展商旗下商場的租戶，他們直指發展商「口爽荷包立」，減幅未如公佈般多，且連正式減租通知也未收到。租戶不願表露身份怕遭報復，有租戶慨嘆，發展商說減幅要待數月後才回撥給他們，坦言「唔知自己等唔等到」；他們認為業界已處於生死存亡關頭，究竟發展商是真心想幫助租戶，還是只做形象工程？揚言要揭穿這些發展商的減租真面目。"},{"pid":"bb0fabbc952878fd0d58455cb63c7cf605fbdfbf","tid":1922290,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lhe9fBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhe9fBn.png&h=1db55097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7Exdn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7Exdn8.png&h=ca414f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61fTHgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61fTHgx.png&h=640ac13c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0f516ffefbc3b3e5188c32e876f891d8ce0487b","tid":1922290,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"新鴻基：示威者行動得啖笑完全對商場業務無影響 上水廣場新年生意人流回升 商戶：生意忙到做到無停手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2549067?=ez\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2549067%3F%3Dez&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=3c5173e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2549067?=ez</a><br />\n<br />\n hket<br />\n現在閱讀<br />\n【香港零售】上水廣場生意「力保不失」 商戶：臨近新年人流回升做到無停手<br />\n【香港零售】上水廣場生意「力保不失」 商戶：臨近新年人流回升做到無停手<br />\n 業界頭條 14:07 2020/01/23 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受社會事件影響，不少商場人流大減，但被視為「水貨客重鎮」的上水廣場人流未有因此而減少，相反臨近農曆新年人流特別多。有商戶指，最近幾日做到「無停手」，預計生意跟去年相若。<br />\n<br />\n人流未有太大影響 近日做到無停手<br />\n<br />\n在上水廣場不時會見到「拖喼客」，甚至會見到他們在店舖門口整理貨品，商場內亦有不少大品牌進駐。在商場內售賣運動鞋的劉小姐指，近幾個月商場的人流沒有太大影響，「除了示威那幾天」，而臨近農曆新年不論是內地客還是本地客都到店舖購物，劉小姐更指最近幾日做到「無停手」，預期生意跟去年同期相若。"},{"pid":"400d435de08cf0b4dab8fbef2cb12fcd2e0eb11a","tid":1922290,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"小租戶批新地：佢哋喺地球上消失咗<br />\n不過，業主與商戶共渡時艱，卻非必然的事。陳與其代表食肆，於過去數月不斷與新地及九倉就減租不停交涉，「佢嘅租務部都會叫我去寫信，但係通常得返嚟嘅回覆都係話冇，尤其是新鴻基，話一毫子都唔會減，而家直頭喺地球上消失咗。」至於九倉，上月有報道指有商戶經磋商多時，終獲減租約半年，減幅約15%至20%，「我就冇受惠嘅，但我知嘅係如果租約就完，呢幾個月減租就會易傾啲。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200108/60460858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60460858&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=545bcd65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60460858&h=0767717d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200108/60460858</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lhe9fBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhe9fBn.png&h=1db55097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7Exdn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7Exdn8.png&h=ca414f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61fTHgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61fTHgx.png&h=640ac13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n信和：依幾個月有出通告話商場唔開既日子先賠租 中間2 3點有示威或防暴商場落閘逼商戶關門趕顧客走既日子全部唔賠<br />\n<br />\n新地：近排已經攪左好多會員推廣吸引人流 唔會減租或免租 之前落閘既日子都唔會賠<br />\n<br />\n10月同11月好多大商場都有好多非大連鎖店既細鋪已經執鳩哂<br />\n可以留意下大商場d冷行已經變哂吉鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大地產商回應商場租戶 話近日社會已經回復平靜 已經無哂周圍破壞同蹤火 商場集會阻礙營業 唔會減租或免租共渡時艱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778223\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dee673acb069942940ff3eb8cda12fbaafe02739","tid":1922290,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"快d欖炒 全部最好1元都唔好減<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1958ae2ab784d136576fbcf45eddb4d06ece9f0","tid":1922290,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}